{"tid":446100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家分享下細個麥當勞既童年回憶","createTime":"2017-10-24T04:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T04:35:08.000Z","uid":150796,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3a023f552be2eb99be424560242dff6da8be1aa3","tid":446100,"uid":150796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:14:20.000Z","msg":"小學個時去左阿嫲屋企訓<br />\n第二朝起身個姑姐叫我落街買包煙<br />\n（個時細路仔都仲可以去報紙檔買煙）<br />\n話淨番啲錢比我買麥當勞食<br />\n個下好似中左六合彩咁開心<br />\n興奮到買左麥當勞唔記得買煙<br />\n番去比人鬧到仆街"},{"pid":"c8c057145822705dce849054d2f2c7b0c74777b2","tid":446100,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5583d8c2da9c3cf1d0538cf31831aa68883d83a1","tid":446100,"uid":39218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:22:45.000Z","msg":"唔記得買煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531ce0ab765242244b412f4c7b8ff7f3e4412d0d","tid":446100,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:26:24.000Z","msg":"記得上m記做過兩次生日<br />\n<br />\n其中一次八號風球，不過都好多人黎左"},{"pid":"cf011f96bcedacebf8f97c5910dc870e51f647d7","tid":446100,"uid":150796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得上m記做過兩次生日<br />\n<br />\n其中一次八號風球，不過都好多人黎左</blockquote><br />\n你就好啦，從來都未試過"},{"pid":"cec4a6003f9697d3aa97a4d64c7383a89c164c74","tid":446100,"uid":149323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d47325144447aada1a6e08c91a6c3cabe579e3","tid":446100,"uid":150796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"仲以為每個香港既細路都鐘意麥記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150f581cdaaad2d6f411ddf97837f86b8f3cd780","tid":446100,"uid":39218,"like":